summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 7.5°C), outside temperature (down 6.4°C), and inside temperature (down 2.3°C), more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 7%), and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.9 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 551 m) and light levels (up 6187 lux).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 1152 m) and light levels (up 8100 lux) when compared to today.
